M|Exam|**Pr|**
M|Exam|tx|> "us want better onboarding."
M|Exam|**So|**
M|Exam|tx|> "Add onboarding."
M|Exam|**Re|**
M|Exam|tx|> "1. Onboarding flow
M|Exam|tx|> 2. Tooltips
M|Exam|tx|> 3. Help doc"
M|Exam|**Wh|**
M|Exam|it|No evidence (who wants this? why?)
M|Exam|it|No personas (who is "us"?)
M|Exam|it|No sc metrics (how do we measure "better"?)
M|Exam|it|No acceptance criteria (what does "onboarding flow" mean?)
M|Exam|it|No st context (why now?)
M|Exam|**Fi|**
M|Exam|- **|** Write problem statement w/ evidence from discovery interviews
M|Exam|- **|** Define persona (Solo Entrepreneur Sam)
M|Exam|- **|** Define sc metrics (activation rate 40% → 60%)
M|Exam|- **|** Break down "onboarding flow" into us stories w/ acceptance criteria
